{"tid":2353481,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[Bitcoin劫案] 柴灣男賣比特幣 遭6南亞賊劫300萬元","createTime":"2021-01-04T19:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T10:24:26.000Z","uid":218407,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"f0de7e1150267bb73cfbca300c92c912d6842a64","tid":2353481,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柴灣發生搶劫案，涉及比特幣交收。昨晚8時許，一名37歲姓李男事主，相約兩名南亞男子，到大潭道興民邨對開交收。<br />\n<br />\n據知他登上對方私家車出售比特幣，對方同場交付現金，他數錢期間有另一輛私家車駛至，4名南亞男子突然打開車門拉事主落車，搶走約300萬現金，並劫去他兩部手機後返回私家車逃去。原先兩名南亞男子亦開車逃去。<br />\n<br />\n事主沒有受傷，立即報案求助，警方到場時已失去南亞賊人蹤影，正調查對方身份及目的。案件列作搶劫。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣為虛疑貨幣，協定數量上限為2,100萬個，於2009年1月3日發行，近兩年價格曾大幅波動，今年3月武漢肺炎疫情期間，一個比特幣價格為4,944.7美元，至今日凌晨2時半，價格已升至每個31,351.85美元，折合港幣約24.31萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210105/B2FDOZXQGVF3ZDVTYDCZCGCHN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210105%2FB2FDOZXQGVF3ZDVTYDCZCGCHN4%2F&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=eacbbcb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210105%2FB2FDOZXQGVF3ZDVTYDCZCGCHN4%2F&h=38cf41bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210105/B2FDOZXQGVF3ZDVTYDCZCGCHN4/</a>"},{"pid":"d8ad2fa97803d538434126062732143e13da9afe","tid":2353481,"uid":181502,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:04:37.000Z","msg":"邊個連登仔啊"},{"pid":"6dae996e54aaafc1bee6974dab15a0a44546ae39","tid":2353481,"uid":27628,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"今朝先睇完呢個post <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2352091\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2352091</a>"},{"pid":"009c8f7bb78c1e9be5895e61af79d30d43e1